                           <note>
                              embedded colophon. It states that the Ms. was written in the time of
                              King Zarʾa Yāʿqob (r. 1434-68), whose throne name was Qʷasṭānṭinos,
                              and of Metropolitan ʾabbā Mikāʾel (s. EAE III, 956-57). In the note,
                              the name &lt;...&gt; Krǝstos (the first part is missing) is mentioned
